'''Trader's Quarter''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on [[Ord Mantell/Legends|Ord Mantell]]. The [[Brawl and Grill]] establishment was there.

[[Callandri]] found [[Alton Lochner]] on Trader's Quarter and attempted to [[Death/Legends|kill]] him. However, Lochner was saved by his friends [[Adazian Liebke]] and [[Tirranna]].

